1.3 External Services Integration
Configure Appwrite for file storage (receipts/documents)
Set up Azure Document Intelligence for OCR
Integrate Plaid API for bank account linking
Set up SendGrid/AWS SES for transactional emails
Configure Sentry for error tracking

1.4 Security Infrastructure
